clutter all over the ground, making it seem like autumn all year round.
No matter how humid the weather may get, the branches and trees always
seem to look more brown rather than the lively green.  That is the
special aura that surrounds this road, an aura magically created by the
wizards long ago.  Traveling south, you will head towards the fabled
market square of midgaard, the north trail leads into northern town.
