Inside the North Gates of Midgaard~
   You are within the safe confines of midgaard, however, once you step
beyond this gate -- You will no longer be protected.  The outside
world offers wild, untame dangers -- yet the excitement and adventures
you will experience will be worth the risks you as an adventurer will
undergo.  Always carry a few extra recalls, potions, weapons and heavy
armor with you at all times.  It's also to your advantage to bring along a
few friends.  Up ahead is a huge stone gate, archers perched on top, ready
to defend the town. Behind you, a trail leads back into the heart of town.
